                                    Monde Selection Awards
                                </div>
                                <div class="txt txt-16 txt-ari title-unit">
                                    (Belgium)
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt txt-inter txt-17 sub">
                                Gold Award for Vinamilk Super Nut (9 Kinds of Nuts), and UHT Fresh Milk.
