                            • Vinamilk - The most chosen dairy and dairy substitutes brand by Vietnamese consumers for the 11th consecutive year. <br><br>
                            • Ông Thọ and Southern Star - The most chosen dairy and dairy substitutes brands by Vietnamese consumers.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box-right">
                        <div class="heading txt-260 txt-bold txt-up number-value">
                            11
                        </div>
                        <div class="heading txt-64 txt-bold number-unit">
                            YEAR
