            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-right">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="txt txt-20 body">
                        CEO of Vinamilk, Ms. Mai Kieu Lien, received the commendation from the Vietnam Association of the Elderly.
                    </div>
                    <div class="heading txt-64 txt-bold sub">
                        “Elderly with excellent economic contribution”
                    </div>
                    <Image src={Chap2Award14} alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-left">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="heading txt-40 txt-bold txt-up title">
                        Top 20 Enterprises meeting Vietnamese business culture standards in 2023
                    </div>
                    <Image src={Chap2Award15} alt="" />
                    <div class="txt txt-14 txt-inter src">
                        (Hiệp hội Phát triển văn hóa Việt Nam)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-right">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="heading txt-40 txt-bold txt-up title">
                        Human Act Prize 2023
                    </div>
                    <div class="txt txt-20 body">
                        • Vinamilk Pathways to Dairy Net Zero program was awarded the “Human Act Prize 2023” - the most important award of the Human Act Prize 2023. <br><br>
                        • Vinamilk's “Stand Tall Vietnam” Milk Fund was honored in the “Sustainable Project” award of the Human Act Prize 2023.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-left">
                <div class="box-img">
                    <Image src={Chap2Award17} alt="" class="img-fill"/>
                    <div class="border"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-right">
                <div class="box-img">
                    <Image src={Chap2Award18} alt="" class="img-fill"/>
                    <div class="border"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-left">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="heading txt-40 txt-bold txt-up title">
                        CSI 2023
                    </div>
                    <div class="list">
                        <div class="list-item">
                            <div class="dot-wrap">
                                <div class="dot"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt txt-20 body">
                                <span class="heading txt-36 txt-bold title">Top 5</span>
                                Pioneers in Embracing Circular Economy and Reducing Carbon Footprint by CSI 2023.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="list-item">
                            <div class="dot-wrap">
                                <div class="dot"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="txt txt-20 body">
                                <span class="heading txt-36 txt-bold title">Top 10</span>
                                Sustainable Enterprises Operating in the Manufacturing Sector by CSI 2023.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-right">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="heading txt-40 txt-bold title">
                        Vietnam Listed Company Awards 2023
                    </div>
                    <div class="list">
                        <div class="txt txt-20 list-item">
                            <div class="dot"></div>
                            <div>First prize for Sustainable Development Report .</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="txt txt-20 list-item">
                            <div class="dot"></div>
                            <div>Awards for Enterprises with Excellent Greenhouse Gas Management.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="txt txt-20 list-item">
                            <div class="dot"></div>
                            <div>Second place in the top 10 Large-cap Companies with Good Corporate Governance.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="txt txt-20 list-item">
                            <div class="dot"></div>
                            <div>Awards for Enterprises Going Beyond Compliance Standards in Corporate Governance.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <Image src={Chap2Award20} alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-left">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <Image src={Chap2Award21} alt="" />
                    <div class="txt txt-20 label">
                        Enterprises with Best Annual Reports in the Non-Financial Sector
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-right">
                <div class="box-content">
                    <div class="txt txt-20 label">
                        Vinamilk's Ông Thọ Condensed Milk received the award for 
                    </div>
                    <div class="heading txt-40 txt-bold txt-up title">
                        The Best Social Media Campaign 
                    </div>
                    <div class="txt txt-14 txt-italic txt-inter src">
                        (Vietnam Creative Advertisements Awards by the Ministry of Culture, Sports, and Tourism).
                    </div>
                    <Image src={Chap2Award22} alt="" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="chap2-award-box" data-aos="fade-up-left">
                <div class="box-img">
                    <Image src={Chap2Award23} alt="" class="img-fill"/>
                    <div class="border"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style lang="scss">
    .chap2-award {
        padding-bottom: 8.2rem;
        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
            padding-bottom: 4.4rem;
        }
        &-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 7.8rem;
            color: var(--cl-blue);
            @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                font-size: 4.2rem;
                line-height: 1em;
                margin-bottom: 3.4rem;
            }
        }
        &-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: var(--grid-gap);
            @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        &-box {
            border-radius: 1.4rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                grid-column: span 1 !important;
            }
            &:nth-child(1) {
                grid-column: span 5;
                background-color: var(--cl-green-dark);
                color: var(--cl-bg);
                .box-content {
                    padding-block: 2.9rem 2.5rem;
                    padding-inline: 2.4rem 3.5rem;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                        padding-block: 1.9rem 1rem;
                        padding-inline: 1.8rem 2rem;
                    }
                    .title {
                        margin-bottom: 4.3rem;
                        line-height: 6rem;
                        margin-right: -1rem;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            margin-bottom: .8rem;
                            margin-inline: -.5rem;
                        }
                    }
                    img {
                        width: 18.5rem;
                        margin-top: -5.2rem;
                        pointer-events: none;
                        margin-left: auto;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            width: 14.4rem;
                            margin-top: -4.8rem;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            &:nth-child(2) {
                grid-column: span 7;
                background-color: var(--cl-green-dark);
                color: var(--cl-bg);
                .box-content {
                    padding-block: 6rem 5.7rem;
                    padding-inline: 4.9rem 4rem;
                    display: flex;
                    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                        padding-block: 2.5rem 1.6rem;
                        padding-inline: 2rem;
                        flex-direction: column;
                        align-items: center;
                    }
                    img {
                        width: 23.8rem;
                        pointer-events: none;
                        margin-right: 2rem;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            margin-right: 0;
                            width: 12rem;
                        }
                    }
                    .list {
                        display: flex;
                        flex-direction: column;
                        justify-content: space-between;
                        padding-block: 1.6rem;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            padding-block: 2rem 0;
                            row-gap: 1.2rem;
                        }
                        .list-item {
                            display: flex;
                            align-items: start;
                            .dot {
                                flex: none;
                                width: 0.4rem;
                                height: 0.4rem;
                                background-color: currentColor;
                                border-radius: 50%;
                                margin-top: 1rem;
                                margin-inline: 1.2rem;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            &:nth-child(3) {
                grid-column: span 5;
                background-color: var(--cl-green);
                color: var(--cl-bg);
                .box-content {
                    padding-block: 2.6rem 3.2rem;
                    padding-inline: 2.4rem 3.5rem;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    position: relative;
                    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                        padding-block: 2.6rem 1.8rem;
                        padding-inline: 2.4rem 8.4rem;
                    }
                    .title {
                        margin-bottom: 4.2rem;
                        line-height: 6rem;
                        max-width: 42rem;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            margin-bottom: 5.2rem;
                        }
                    }
                    img {
                        position: absolute;
                        width: 14.5rem;
                        right: 0;
                        bottom: 0;
                        pointer-events: none;
                    }
                }
                
            }
            &:nth-child(4) {
                grid-column: span 7;
                background-color: var(--cl-red-man);
                color: var(--cl-bg);
                .box-content {
                    padding-block: 2.6rem 3.2rem;
                    padding-inline: 4.2rem 4.2rem;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    position: relative;
                    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                        padding-block: 16rem 1.5rem;
                        padding-inline: 2.5rem;
                    }
                    .title {
                        margin-bottom: 4.2rem;
                        line-height: 6rem;
                        max-width: 37rem;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            max-width: 26.4rem;
                            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
                        }
                    }
                    img {
                        position: absolute;
                        width: 20.8rem;
                        right: 5.7rem;
                        top: 1.4rem;
                        pointer-events: none;
                        @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
                            top: 0;
                            width: 19.2rem;
                            right: 7.6rem;
                        }
                    }
                }
                
            }
            &:nth-child(5) {
                grid-column: span 5;
                background-color: var(--cl-pink-main);
                color: var(--cl-bg);
